el).\",\n   777→        \"PDA seeds: [b\\\"match\\\", creator.key().as_ref(), &nonce.to_le_bytes()]\"\n   778→      ],\n   779→      \"type\": {\n   780→        \"kind\": \"struct\",\n   781→        \"fields\": [\n   782→          {\n   783→            \"name\": \"creator\",\n   784→            \"docs\": [\n   785→              \"The player who created the match.\"\n   786→            ],\n   787→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   788→          },\n   789→          {\n   790→            \"name\": \"opponent\",\n   791→            \"docs\": [\n   792→              \"The player who joined (Pubkey::default() if empty).\"\n   793→            ],\n   794→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   795→          },\n   796→          {\n   797→            \"name\": \"server\",\n   798→            \"docs\": [\n   799→              \"Server key that co-signed create and will settle.\"\n   800→            ],\n   801→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   802→          },\n   803→          {\n   804→            \"name\": \"tier\",\n   805→            \"docs\": [\n   806→              \"Tier index (0-7).\"\n   807→            ],\n   808→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n   809→          },\n   810→          {\n   811→            \"name\": \"entry_amount\",\n   812→            \"docs\": [\n   813→              \"Entry amount in lamports (derived from tier).\"\n   814→            ],\n   815→            \"type\": \"u64\"\n   816→          },\n   817→          {\n   818→            \"name\": \"creator_side\",\n   819→            \"docs\": [\n   820→              \"Side chosen by creator (0 = Heads, 1 = Tails).\"\n   821→            ],\n   822→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n   823→          },\n   824→          {\n   825→            \"name\": \"phase\",\n   826→            \"docs\": [\n   827→              \"Current phase (0=Waiting, 1=Locked, 2=Settled, 3=Refunded).\"\n   828→            ],\n   829→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n   830→          },\n   831→          {\n   832→            \"name\"